<paragraph id="613633DA0346273293A383A9DD04EEC8" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">
Namibia (Fig. 
<figureCitation id="9727B0EAF524CE3860BCF667DEC400AD" captionStart="Figure 36" captionStartId="F11" captionText="Figure 36. Distribution map for Pampsilota afer, Pampsilota africanus, Pampsilota brandbergensis, and Pampsilota dahomeyanus." figureDoi="10.3897/dez.64.10800.figure36" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118804" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">36</figureCitation>
